EN: She holds great respect for this teacher.

ZH: 他敬爱着这位领袖。
EN: He admires this leader greatly.

ZH: 我们应该敬爱大自然。
EN: We should respect and cherish nature.

ZH: 敬爱他人是我们的美德之一。
EN: Respecting others is one of our virtues.

ZH: 在这个社会，应该互相敬爱。
EN: In this society, we should respect each other.

ZH: 我们要向那些为社会做出贡献的人敬爱。
EN: We should show respect to those who contribute to society.

ZH: 敬爱是一种美德。
EN: Respect is a virtue.

ZH: 作为一个领袖，他敬爱每一位成员。
EN: As a leader, he respects every member.

ZH: 这位科学家受到世人的敬爱。
EN: This scientist is respected by everyone.

ZH: 敬爱他人可以建立友谊。
EN: Respecting others can build friendships.

ZH: 她对艺术家们充满着敬爱之心。
EN: She has a deep admiration for artists.

